```julia
function lotka_volterra!(du,u,p,t)
    du[1] = - p[1]*u[1]*u[2] + p[2]*u[1]
    du[2] = p[3]*u[1]*u[2] - p[4]*u[2]
end

u0 = [10.0, 7.0]
p = [0.3, 2.0, 0.4, 3.0]
tspan = (0.0, 10.0)
```
